      • LAST_EXPIRY_NOTIFICATION_PROPNAME

        static final java.lang.String LAST_EXPIRY_NOTIFICATION_PROPNAME
        The property name to keep the time of last asset expiration notification service run. It will be updated with current date after each service notification. Notifications will be sent for all assets which are getting expired between LAST_EXPIRY_NOTIFICATION_PROPNAME and current date.
